<h2> Micro-biome</h2>
<h5 style="text-align:left;">The foreign inhabitant - the microbiome is the entire ecosystem of microbes living inside our body. The genetic material of all microorganisms- bacteria, fungi, yeast, moulds & viruses forms a living layer over your skin and parts of the inside of your body, including the lungs and the digestive tract, from the mouth all the way down to the colon through the vagus nerve.

When our gut microbe is out of balance, our immune system is out of balance since 70% of our immune system is along the gut lining. When our immune system is out of balance, our body is not at ease. This results in inflammation, the root cause of all chronic diseases.</h5></div> </div>

<div class=" w3-padding-8 w3-container w3-white w3-center">
  <div class="w3-content">
<h5 style="text-align:left;">We would like to introduce you to this unique microbial world living inside your body, how these microorganisms coordinate with various organs of your body, educate you on what is exactly happening inside your body, & optimise them to make them start working in your favor.

We quantify & magnify living organisms in your gut & evaluate your current gut ecosystem to determine whether the food metabolised by your gut bacteria will release essential nutrients or toxins in your bloodstream which will inflammate your body.</h5></div>

